name: effective_time
description: Points to a column which represents the effective time of a row in a dimension node. Used to facilitate proper joins with fact nodes on event time.

name: primary_key
description: Points to a column which is part of the primary key of the node

name: dimension
description: Points to a dimension attribute column

name: expired_time
description: Points to a column which represents the expired time of a row in a dimension node. Used to facilitate proper joins with fact nodes on event time.

name: event_time
description: Points to a column which represents the time of the event in a given fact related node. Used to facilitate proper joins with dimension node to match the desired effect.
